        "experience.job0.title": "AI R&D Software Engineer Intern",
        "experience.job0.desc.p1": "At Evident Scientific in Québec, I worked on an end-to-end module for evaluating AI models dedicated to segmentation and anomaly detection, integrated into a large Python desktop application.",
