        "experience.job2.desc.p2": "<li>Redesigned the application with React.js, Express.js, and MongoDB to improve scalability and performance.</li><li>Analyzed business needs and translated them into technical specifications.</li><li>Created UI/UX prototypes on Figma for the new front-end architecture.</li><li>Collaborated with the project team to align design, user experience, and business logic.</li>",
