        "experience.job3.desc.p1": "Within the IT department of Cambrai City Hall, I supported users and took part in day-to-day municipal IT operations.",
        "experience.job3.desc.p2": "<li>Provided technical support to city employees.</li><li>Participated in the optimization of the city's network infrastructure.</li><li>Worked with the IT team to understand operational constraints and infrastructure needs.</li>",
